            release: { tr: "<strong>Play Console</strong>'da <strong>Internal testing</strong> (max 100 kişi) veya <strong>Closed testing</strong> track'i ile en az 5-10 dış test kullanıcısına ulaştırıldı, geri bildirim alındı. <strong>Google Play Developer</strong> hesabı aktif ($25 tek seferlik). İçerik derecelendirmesi (IARC), <strong>Data safety</strong> formu ve gizlilik beyanı tamamlandı.", en: "Reached at least 5-10 external testers via <strong>Play Console</strong>'s <strong>Internal testing</strong> (up to 100 people) or <strong>Closed testing</strong> track; feedback collected. <strong>Google Play Developer</strong> account is active ($25 one-time). Content rating (IARC), <strong>Data safety</strong> form and privacy declaration complete." }
