        mvp: { tr: "<strong>Firebase Remote Config</strong> (veya alternatif: PostHog Feature Flags, GrowthBook, Statsig, LaunchDarkly) entegre. En az bir özellik <strong>feature flag</strong> arkasında: konsoldan açılıp kapatılabiliyor, yeni build gerekmiyor. <span class='hint'>11.3 release'deki staged rollout'la doğal eşleşir: önce %1, sonra %10 vs. PWA'da feature flag özellikle değerli çünkü deploy saniyelik.</span>", en: "<strong>Firebase Remote Config</strong> (or alternatives: PostHog Feature Flags, GrowthBook, Statsig, LaunchDarkly) is integrated. At least one feature is behind a <strong>feature flag</strong>: it can be toggled from the console with no new build. <span class='hint'>This pairs naturally with staged rollouts in 11.3 release: 1% first, then 10%, etc. On PWA feature flags are especially valuable because deploys are instant.</span>" },
